                        </p>
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 border-top pt-3" style="border-top-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05) !important;">
                            <span class="rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-white font-outfit" style="width: 38px; height: 38px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4F6EF7 0%, #8B5CF6 100%); font-weight: 700; font-size: 13px;">NT</span>
                            <div>
                                <h6 class="text-white mb-0" style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 13px;">Nguyễn Thanh Trung</h6>
                                <span class="text-warning" style="font-size: 11px;"><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i> 5.0</span>
